About Event

​Join us as we celebrate the opening of our one-of-a-kind Residential Eating Disorder Treatment program!

​Come and learn more about the latest treatments for Eating Disorders, enjoy a tour of our one-of-a-kind facility, the luxe PHP with supportive housing apartments, and the beautiful natural surroundings. Bring colleagues, friends or family and make a day of it on the incredible San Mateo County coast. You will re-connect with old friends and gather with new ones!
